Graphic view of the total Hamiltonian.
 In blue, the atomic 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{at}}^{\parallel}$
\end_inset

, the medium 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\mathrm{m}}^{\parallel}$
\end_inset

 [Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


