\end_inset

] Hamiltonians.
 The blue blocks are connected by the interaction blocks.
 Hence 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{\textrm{m}}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{\textrm{at}}$
\end_inset

 connect the medium and the atom, respectively, with the field as in Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
