noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 depicts the thirteen allowed transitions from a selected manifold 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)$
\end_inset

, corresponding to different parts of the Hamiltonian, connecting respectively
 the 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)\rightarrow\mathcal{E}\left(n-1\right)$
\end_inset

 manifolds (the JC interaction term, green arrows), 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)\rightarrow\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)\rightarrow\mathcal{E}\left(n-2\right)$
\end_inset

 manifolds (the AS Hamiltonian, purple arrows), 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{E}\left(n\right)\rightarrow\mathcal{E}\left(n-3\right)$
\end_inset

 manifolds (the CR contribution, red arrows).
\end_layout

