\end_inset

depends only on 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{R}/\omega_{c}$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $n=10$
\end_inset

, for the resonant case 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{a}=\omega_{c}$
\end_inset

 (a) and far from the resonance case 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\omega_{c}-\omega_{a}\right)/\omega_{c}=0.2$
\end_inset

 (b).

\color black
 Around 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{R}=0.16\omega_{c}$
\end_inset

 on the left or 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{R}=0.19\omega_{c}$
\end_inset

 on the right indicate the first energy crossings according to the JC model.
 For coupling constants beyond these values the structure of the energy
 ladder from Fig.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
