\begin_inset Formula $\left|\left\langle f_{\phi}|a|i_{\iota}\right\rangle \right|^{2}$
\end_inset

.
 Colors indicate different transition mechanisms: the Jaynes-Cummings transition
 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|10_{+}\right\rangle \to\left|9_{+}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 is shown in green, the counter-rotating term 
